\c 33
\s Jehovha anoramba kuenda neVaIsraeri, asi Mozisi anovanyengeterera
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehovha wakati kuna Mozisi: Enda, kwira kubva pano, iwe nevanhu vawakakwidza kubva munyika yeEgipita\x + 32.7.\x*, uende kunyika yandakapikira kuna Abhurahama, kuna Isaka, nekuna Jakove, ndichiti: Kumbeu yako ndichaipa\x + Gen.. 12.7; Eki. 32.13.\x*.
\v 2 Uye ndichatuma mutumwa pamberi penyu\x + 32.34.\x*, ndigodzinga VaKenani, VaAmori, neVaHiti, neVaPerezi, VaHivhi, neVaJebhusi\x + 13.5.\x*,
\v 3 muende kunyika inoyerera mukaka neuchi\x + 3.8.\x*; nokuti handingakwiri pakati penyu\x + 33.15-17.\x*, nokuti muri vanhu vemitsipa mikukutu\x + 32.9.\x*; zvimwe ndingakupedzai panzira\x + 32.10. Num.. 16.21,45.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Vanhu vakati vachinzwa shoko iri rakaipa, vakachema\x + Num.. 14.39.\x*; uye hakuna munhu wakaisa paari zvishongo zvake\x + Eze. 24.17,23. 26.16.\x*.
\v 5 Nokuti Jehovha wakati kuna Mozisi: Iti kuvana vaIsraeri: Muri vanhu vemitsipa mikukutu\x + 33.3.\x*; ndikakwira pakati penyu chinguvana ndingakupedzai; naizvozvo ikozvino\x + Num.. 16.21.\x* bvisai\x + 32.12.\x* zvishongo zvenyu zvibve kwamuri, ndizive chandingakuitirai.
\v 6 Zvino vana vaIsraeri vakazvikurura zvishongo zvavo kubva pagomo reHorebhu.
\p
\v 7 Zvino Mozisi wakatora tende, ndokuridzika kunze kwemusasa, kure nemusasa, ndokuritumidza \add kuti\add* tende rekusangana. Zvino\x + 29.42,43.\x* zvakaitika kuti umwe neumwe waitsvaka\x + 1 Makor. 16.10. Map. 40.16.\x* Jehovha waibudira kutende rekusangana, raiva riri kunze kwemusasa.
\v 8 Zvino zvakaitika pakubudira kwaMozisi kutende, \add kuti\add* vanhu vose vaisimuka ndokumira umwe neumwe pamukova wetende rake\x + Num.. 16.27.\x*, vakatarira shure kwaMozisi kusvika apinda mutende.
\v 9 Zvino zvakaitika pakupinda kwaMozisi mutende, shongwe yegore yaiburuka imire pamukova\x + 13.21; Map. 99.7.\x* wetende; \add Jehovha\add* ndokutaura naMozisi\x + 13.21, Map. 99.7.\x*.
\v 10 Vanhu vose ndokuona shongwe yegore imire pamukova wetende, vanhu vose ndokusimuka vakanamata\x + 4.31. 12.27. 34.8.\x* umwe neumwe pamukova wetende rake.
\v 11 Zvino Jehovha waitaura naMozisi chiso nechiso\x + Num.. 12.8. Det. 34.10. Gen.. 32.30.\x*, semunhu anotaura kushamwari yake. Otendeukirazve kumusasa; asi muranda\x + 17.9. 24.13. 32.17.\x* wake Joshua, mwanakomana waNuni, mujaya, waiva asingabvi mukati metende.
\p
\v 12 Zvino Mozisi wakati kuna Jehovha: Tarirai, makati kwandiri: Kwira nevanhu ava, asi\x + 32.34.\x* imwi hamuna kundizivisa wamuchatuma neni. Zvakadaro imwi makati: Ndinokuziva nezita\x + 33.17.\x*, uye wakawanawo nyasha pameso angu\x + 33.12,16,17. 34.9.\x*.
\v 13 Zvino ikozvino kana ndakawana hangu nyasha pameso enyu, ndizivisei henyu nzira\x + Map.25.4. 119.33.\x* yenyu, kuti ndikuzivei, kuti ndiwane nyasha pameso enyu; uye onai kuti rudzi urwu vanhu venyu\x + Det. 9.29. Jow. 2.17.\x*.
\v 14 Zvino \add Jehovha\add* wakati: Kuvapo kwangu kuchaenda \add newe\add*\x + 40.34-38. Isa. 63.9.\x*, ndigokupa zororo\x + Det. 3.20. Josh. 21.44. 22.4. 23.1. Map. 95.11.\x*.
\v 15 Iye ndokuti kwaari: Kana kuvapo kwenyu kusingaendi \add neni\add*, musatikwidza kubva pano\x + 33.1,2,3.\x*.
\v 16 Nokuti zvichazikanwawo sei kuti ndakawana nyasha pameso enyu, ini nevanhu venyu? Hakuzi kuti muende nesu here? Zvino\x + Num.. 14.14.\x* tive vakatsaurwa, ini\x + 1 Madz. 8.53.\x* nevanhu venyu, kubva pavanhu vose vari pachiso chenyika.
\v 17 Jehovha ndokuti kuna Mozisi: Ndichaitawo chinhu ichi chawareva, nokuti wawana nyasha pameso angu\x + 33.13.\x*, uye ndinokuziva nezita\x + 33.12.\x*.
\v 18 Iye ndokuti: Ndiratidzei henyu kubwinya kwenyu\x + 33.20.\x*.
\v 19 \add Jehovha\add* ndokuti: Ini ndichapfuudza kunaka kwangu kwese pamberi pechiso\x + Map. 31.19. Jer. 31.14. 34.5-7.\x* chako, uye ndichadanidzira zita raJehovha pamberi pako. Zvino ndichanzwira nyasha wandichanzwira nyasha, uye\x + VaRom. 9.15.\x* ndichanzwira tsitsi wandichanzwira tsitsi\x + VaRom. 4.4. 9.16,18.\x*.
\v 20 Akatiwo: Haugoni kuona chiso changu, nokuti munhu haangandioni akararama\x + Gen.. 32.30. Det. 5.24. Vato. 6.22,23. 13.22. Isa. 6.5. Zvak. 1.16,17. 24.10.\x*.
\v 21 Jehovha akatiwo: Tarira pane nzvimbo kwandiri pauchamira pabwe.
\v 22 Zvino zvichaitika pachapfuura kubwinya kwangu kuti ndichakuisa mumukaha webwe\x + Isa. 2.21.\x*, ndigokufukidza neruoko rwangu ndichipfuura\x + Map. 91.4.\x*.
\v 23 Zvino ndichabvisa ruoko rwangu, ugoona zveshure kwangu; asi chiso changu hachionekwi\x + 33.20. Joh. 1.18. 1 Tim. 6.16. 1 Joh. 4.12.\x*.